# Node / pnpm
node_modules/
.pnpm-store/
# package-lock.json is committed — `npm ci` in CI requires it and it is the
# single source of truth for exact versions + sha512 integrity hashes that
# pin our supply chain (jsdom, playwright, react, etc.).

